        <num>CC 2692</num>
        <heading>2692.  Lessee's obligation to make repairs</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2692.  Lessee's obligation to make repairs
The lessee is bound to repair damage to the thing caused by his fault or that of persons who, with his consent, are on the premises or use the thing, and to repair any deterioration resulting from his or their use to the extent it exceeds the normal or agreed use of the thing.</p>
        </content>
